Given that this {{IPAchar|/s/}} only ever appears interstitially, and given the semantics, this {{IPAchar|/s/}} may be cognate with {{cog|ko|-}} interfix {{m|ko|-ㅅ-}} used to mark possession; compare {{nc|de|-s-}}.

